{
  "analysis": "The 5fps frame extraction succeeded (951 frames), but the OCR script was not created because the heredoc was mangled. No solution.txt has been written yet. We need safely create a fast bottom-crop OCR script for the 951 frames, run it, and then build/validate the move list against the ending's explicit 262 moves.",
  "plan": "Use `printf` to create `/app/work/bottom5_ocr.py` robustly without a heredoc. The script will crop the active bottom region (y=635-720), scale it 3x, grayscale/binarize, and OCR all 951 frames. Then verify the file exists and run it with polling, because full-size OCR on 951 frames is too slow and the bottom crop is sufficient for prompt/input extraction.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "printf '%s\\n' 'from PIL import Image, ImageOps' 'import pytesseract, glob, os' 'fs=sorted(glob.glob(\"/app/work/frames5/frame_*.png\"), key=lambda p:int(os.path.basename(p).split(\"_\")[1].split(\".\")[0]))' 'os.makedirs(\"/app/work/bottom5\", exist_ok=True)' 'for n,p in enumerate(fs,1):' '    im=Image.open(p)' '    crop=im.crop((0,635,1280,720))' '    crop=crop.resize((crop.width*3, crop.height*3))' '    g=ImageOps.grayscale(crop)' '    bw=g.point(lambda v:0 if v<140 else 255,\"1\")' '    txt=pytesseract.image_to_string(bw, config=\"--psm 6\")' '    out=\"/app/work/bottom5/\"+os.path.basename(p).replace(\".png\",\".txt\")' '    open(out,\"w\").write(txt)' '    if n%50==0:' '        print(\"bottom5\",n,\"of\",len(fs),flush=True)' 'print(\"bottom5 files\",len(fs))' > /app/work/bottom5_ocr.py\n",
      "duration": 0.1
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "ls -l /app/work/bottom5_ocr.py; head -5 /app/work/bottom5_ocr.py\n",
      "duration": 0.1
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "nohup python3 /app/work/bottom5_ocr.py > /app/work/logs/bottom5_ocr.out 2>&1 & echo $! > /app/work/logs/bottom5_ocr.pid; cat /app/work/logs/bottom5_ocr.pid\n",
      "duration": 60.0
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "cat /app/work/logs/bottom5_ocr.out; echo '---'; ls /app/work/bottom5 2>/dev/null | wc -l; ps -p $(cat /app/work/logs/bottom5_ocr.pid) -o pid,etime,cmd || true\n",
      "duration": 0.1
    }
  ]
}
